headline: Deutsche Bank ups Digital Realty Trust to Buy on robust demand, growth visibility
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank (ETR:DBKGn) upgraded shares of Digital Realty (NYSE:DLR) Trust to Buy and lifted the target price to $194 from $185. The company’s shares rose 1.5% in premarket trading Wednesday.
